                    </p>
                    <p>
                        If your employer requires personal protective equipment, such as hard hats, safety shoes, safety glasses, respirators, or hearing protection, you are responsible to wear and/or use the equipment.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        If you do not know how to safely use tools, equipment or machinery, be sure to ask your supervisor.
                    </p>
                    <p>
